						               													<description>Portals is a fun and strategic card game where you can create your own deck to battle your friends.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Portals you battle against each other with 3 pre-chosen Champion cards to breach your opponents Stronghold represented by Breach Points. You can lower your opponent's Breach Points by battling his Champions and by opening Portals that can transfer you to other realms! &amp;#10;But beware, Champions can get stronger during the game, so watch your back!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Portals is a TCG where you create your own deck to play. Choose your 3 Champions to build your deck around, take the mutual Portal cards and place them in three piles between you and your opponent. You start with 4 cards in your hand. During your turn, you can play as many cards as you like and you may use every Champion for their attack and effect once, if you pay their Stamina cost. If a certain condition of your Champion is met, it gets empowered! This can change their stats and/or its effect. But watch out! Your Champions Breach points go up as well. So, if they get defeated you lose that many more.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Big part of the game is opening Portals. Every Portal has a specific cost. By gathering enough allies from your deck in the corresponding zone, you can open the Portals and send them through to gain different effects and breach your enemy's Stronghold.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
